      "date": "2018-05-01 22:02:49.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified+1\n\nTests uploaded by AT Release Candidate from trevis-66vm1 for review-ldiskfs received by maloo, run on CentOS Linux 7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/e0f3c1b0-04ad-4d65-a225-fe330076a572). Ran 5 tests. No failures.",
